{"tid":695801,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"長澤雅美造型崩壞！網友大驚「是苗可麗」","createTime":"2018-06-09T13:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T16:20:22.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9bf70095a067f4ad29cc1afb6a05cf7192805c","tid":695801,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"31歲日本女星長澤雅美昨日（7日）在東京出席台灣觀光局舉辦的「夏天台灣觀光~SUMMER FORMOSA」代言記者會，她身穿紅金色系的長禮服亮相，透露造型是以台灣的形象所挑選，對於成為首位連續2年擔任台灣觀光代言人的日本藝人，但是造型讓網友傻眼，更有人直呼：「是苗可麗！」<br />\n<br />\n長澤雅美出席觀光局在日本東京舉辦的活動，她一改昔日甜美模樣，剪了露耳的短頭髮，再畫上豔麗的大紅唇，身穿一襲紅色連身長裙現身，但造型卻不被台灣網友買單。就有鄉民在《PTT》發文，表示「長澤雅美壞掉了！」隨即引起熱烈討論，不少人紛紛表示是不是得罪造型師，甚至更有人笑稱「是苗可麗！」<br />\n<br />\n對此，有許多網友認為長澤雅美這次的髮型是最大的問題點，一語道破「短髮會讓大餅臉超明顯」、「幫她畫長髮會不會好點」、「大餅臉還剪這樣」、「長髮比較正，短髮變肉餅臉」、「衣服也顯得水桶腰」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180608/640_742e68d93afbe4bf87d06c2d38be3b05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180608%2F640_742e68d93afbe4bf87d06c2d38be3b05.jpg&h=bf21191c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長澤雅美。翻攝Crankin網站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180608/640_4263816949231beb3d2d098b3c973dec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180608%2F640_4263816949231beb3d2d098b3c973dec.jpg&h=8d2a18bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長澤雅美。翻攝《報知體育報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19598845_796938040486992_6866105764808504578_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=ad68f767dbd23f001ee0d0ad1564fb97&amp;oe=5BAAAD01\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19598845_796938040486992_6866105764808504578_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Dad68f767dbd23f001ee0d0ad1564fb97%26oe%3D5BAAAD01&h=f8cbec83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪即將步入30歲。翻攝google網站"},{"pid":"7627a309fcf3d1e4e7259fdf02e9ccc3fc3c9f60","tid":695801,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"照屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db05d348fd850f33f63803fc4d6f17071b467c7c","tid":695801,"uid":53886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5c43f24e62e2d77a07f2943e7b001b80532e8a","tid":695801,"uid":152123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.walkerplus.com/article/144954/819153_615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.walkerplus.com%2Farticle%2F144954%2F819153_615.jpg&h=8161d06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n髮型同個妝嘅問題 呢套劇仲係好正常<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newscafe.ne.jp/imgs/p/HSrphxnonnO2frczedsZFbfS6t2y3dzb2tnY/3465970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscafe.ne.jp%2Fimgs%2Fp%2FHSrphxnonnO2frczedsZFbfS6t2y3dzb2tnY%2F3465970.jpg&h=7a1b1e9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c88f6b851a5ed091ae2b472551bbea3b3ed3e192","tid":695801,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"有幾崩<br />\n不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5a5175b06c51d0f30d572dbea0852e92fadfd8","tid":695801,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"邊位呀阿嬸"},{"pid":"386cfa1e8574b0c4b9207a1f8d523315958781d5","tid":695801,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c88f6b851a5ed091ae2b472551bbea3b3ed3e192","tid":695801,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"有幾崩<br />\n不知幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-0